snippet.title: Pac-Man - Xbox 360
snippet.description:
Hi! It's really cool that one can buy certain classical games on 360, 'Now' again it's really tough to play those games using the 360 controller and this one is on exception, especially when you are not good at playing the games. I never played enough to past 3 levels........ I just bought it because I like to have it that's it.
